	<div class="ibox-image"></div>
</div> 
<p>白 (bái) doesn't only mean "white." When added before a verb it means to do that verb "in vain" or "with no effect."
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="Expressing_wasted_efforts_with_&quot;bai&quot;#Basic_Form_with_Just_.E7.99.BD"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">Basic Form with Just 白</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-2"><a href="Expressing_wasted_efforts_with_&quot;bai&quot;#Structure"><span class="tocnumber">1.1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-3"><a href="Expressing_wasted_efforts_with_&quot;bai&quot;#Examples"><span class="tocnumber">1.2</span> <span class="toctext">Examples</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-4"><a href="Expressing_wasted_efforts_with_&quot;bai&quot;#Form_with_.E7.99.BD.E7.99.BD"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Form with 白白</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="Expressing_wasted_efforts_with_&quot;bai&quot;#Structure_2"><span class="tocnumber">2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-6"><a href="Expressing_wasted_efforts_with_&quot;bai&quot;#Examples_2"><span class="tocnumber">2.2</span> <span class="toctext">Examples</span></a></li>
</ul>
</li>
